    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Triangle: Cursed Town 是一款 1–4 人在线合作驱魔恐怖游戏，背景设定在一个被封锁、废弃的村庄。接连发生失踪事件后，你和你的队伍受教会派遣，去调查被埋在村庄沉默之下的真相。道路封闭，村民消失，留下的只有诅咒……以及仍在以此为食的存在。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>调查</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入你选择的闹鬼地点，与队友一起收集证据。村庄不会免费给你答案，你在里面多待一分钟，风险就更高。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/b4b0cbfa63060f8b4d1783e76c8668ec.poster.avif?t=1767405234\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/b4b0cbfa63060f8b4d1783e76c8668ec.webm?t=1767405234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>识别实体</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用你找到的线索判断你面对的是什么。直面 <strong>20 种实体类型</strong>，每一种都会带来不同的风险与反应。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/07924da16eba47dcdf1981fb0e470fd5.poster.avif?t=1767405234\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/07924da16eba47dcdf1981fb0e470fd5.webm?t=1767405234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/07924da16eba47dcdf1981fb0e470fd5.mp4?t=1767405234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>完成仪式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到所需的仪式物品，布置仪式区域，并在压力之下按步骤完成。<strong>你停留得越久，恶魔就越愤怒——所以要快。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/f831942737d1f5cc10fe060e0be6abb7.poster.avif?t=1767405234\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/f831942737d1f5cc10fe060e0be6abb7.webm?t=1767405234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>合作恐怖</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人游玩或最多 4 人合作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沟通与时机至关重要</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失误会带来后果<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/d2c93c5e000f7e6e3d369069762cd31e.poster.avif?t=1767405234\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266950/extras/d2c93c5e000f7e6e3d369069762cd31e.webm?t=1767405234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
